# HopeTSIT — Terms of Service

Version 1.0 — Effective date: upon first publication to app stores.

## 1. Preamble and definitions

These Terms of Service ("Terms") govern access to and use of the HopeTSIT mobile application and platform (the "Service"). The Service is a technical intermediary connecting pet owners ("Petowners") and pet sitters ("Petsitters"), collectively "Users".

"Platform" means the HopeTSIT app, its backend, the admin dashboard and all related services. "Booking" means a service agreed between a Petowner and a Petsitter. "Payment" means the sum paid by the Petowner for a Booking via the Stripe payment processor.

## 2. Acceptance of the Terms

By creating an account and using the Service, each User expressly accepts the current version of these Terms. The acceptance date and version are logged on the server. Continued use after a version change implies acceptance of the new Terms (see section 22).

## 3. Publisher identification

The Service is operated by **CARDELLI HERMANOS LIMITED** (company number 2671528), registered office at Flat/RM A 12/F ZJ 300, 300 Lockhart Road, Wan Chai, Hong Kong. Customer service contact: **hopetsit@gmail.com**.

