Within the maximum limits of applicable law, CARDELLI HERMANOS LIMITED's liability is excluded for any indirect damage, loss of profit, loss of data, or commercial damage. In any event, the maximum aggregate liability of CARDELLI HERMANOS LIMITED is capped at the amount of the User's most recent transaction via the Platform. Force-majeure events suspend all obligations.

