## 21. Customer service

For any question or complaint, please contact **hopetsit@gmail.com**. An initial response is provided within 5 business days.

## 22. Modification of the Terms

HopeTSIT may modify these Terms. A **30-day notice** is sent to active Users before the new version enters into force. Continued use beyond this period implies acceptance of the new version. A User refusing the new version may terminate their account as provided in section 18.
